    "description": "通过<strong>Aquatic Store Simulator</strong>进入充满活力的水生零售世界！接受管理您自己的水下主题超市的挑战，将业务管理与水生生物的美丽融为一体。在货架上摆放奇异的鱼类和装饰品，设定价格，收款并维护水族馆。运送鱼类，处理交易，并确保您的客户满意。定制和扩展您的商店，成为终极水族企业家。<br><br>🏪 <strong>管理您自己的水生超市：</strong> 建立和定制您的商店，为客户和海洋生物创造一个天堂。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/d604033f22f11d478839f8c58ad4f118.poster.avif?t=1772059061\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/d604033f22f11d478839f8c58ad4f118.webm?t=1772059061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/d604033f22f11d478839f8c58ad4f118.mp4?t=1772059061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>📦 <strong>产品展示：</strong> 战略性地放置商品以吸引客户。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/52f7268b183a3340f165d1ad6063ad51.poster.avif?t=1772059061\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/52f7268b183a3340f165d1ad6063ad51.webm?t=1772059061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/52f7268b183a3340f165d1ad6063ad51.mp4?t=1772059061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>💲 <strong>定价：</strong>调整价格以优化销售和客户满意度。<br><br>🐠 <strong>水族馆准备：</strong>设置和维护养鱼的水族馆，确保它们的健康和快乐，与其他超市或宠物店游戏相比，这是一个突出的特点。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/d0f0345ef863a35a7325174dbd45e853.poster.avif?t=1772059061\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/d0f0345ef863a35a7325174dbd45e853.webm?t=1772059061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/d0f0345ef863a35a7325174dbd45e853.mp4?t=1772059061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🚚 <strong>鱼类配送：</strong>将选定的鱼类送到客户手中，提升他们的购物体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/29843d3cef6c30738d94759ae409610d.poster.avif?t=1772059061\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/29843d3cef6c30738d94759ae409610d.webm?t=1772059061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/29843d3cef6c30738d94759ae409610d.mp4?t=1772059061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🏧 <strong>结账操作：</strong>处理客户交易并准确提供零钱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/6e5275321aa383c9ac1eedfaa27f30e2.poster.avif?t=1772059061\" width=610 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/6e5275321aa383c9ac1eedfaa27f30e2.webm?t=1772059061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073580/extras/6e5275321aa383c9ac1eedfaa27f30e2.mp4?t=1772059061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🌟 <strong>大量库存</strong>：利用大约 500 种物品（包括各种鱼类和装饰品）来储存您的商店。<br><br><strong>是什么让我们在“市场”模拟游戏中脱颖而出：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>具有高级水族方面（繁殖、护理、装饰）的主题超市<br></li><li>有形物品的真实销售体验<br></li><li>超过 500 种物品的丰富库存可在游戏中使用</li></ul><br>将您的商店变成一个繁荣的水生活动中心，成为终极水族企业家。体验水上超市模拟器中商业管理和水下冒险的完美结合！",
